metadata.name: NyanPunk #1
metadata.description: NyanPunks is an NFT collection inspired by the beloved Nyan Cat and iconic CryptoPunks. This limited edition series features 10,000 individually designed NFTs, each showcasing a quirky and playful cat-themed design. With NyanPunks, you can add a touch of fun and cuteness to your digital asset collection and show your love for the iconic Nyan Cat and CryptoPunks.
